{"tid":238813,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視體育被入稟 追收107萬廣告費","createTime":"2017-05-11T09:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T10:24:12.000Z","uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f18848c9b3709ce13a6832222012b393ff158cf5","tid":238813,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T09:12:35.000Z","msg":"根據提交香港高等法院的傳票，Polarline Development稱其為樂視體育文化產業發展（香港）有限公司，提供了展示型廣告服務。<br />\n<br />\n文件指，樂視去年8-9月，預訂了香港七個站點的展示標識。Polarline指，工作已經完成，但雖幾經催討，樂視體育一直沒有與其結算，兩筆總計107萬港元的款項。Polarline入稟要求索償。"},{"pid":"801c5ea7787fb59bc38b4bb9a9c465b90341d46e","tid":238813,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T09:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773fc1ffbf796a99ad1e1391618011af182c8c62","tid":238813,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"好彩簽左now<br />\n樂視份份鍾下季都頂唔住"},{"pid":"2954ec88d23c896ad983892e322980b1aa1ddbd7","tid":238813,"uid":53897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩簽左now<br />\n樂視份份鍾下季都頂唔住</blockquote><br />\nNOW都係轉播樂視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690b385da39e44c70ecc7de429f689e3d2d8e58e","tid":238813,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好彩簽左now<br />\n樂視份份鍾下季都頂唔住</blockquote><br />\nNOW都係轉播樂視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢播唔到即係毀約 再拎出黎投都會係now播"}]}